imdb.plot outline: Financial expert Mary Caraccioli travels across the country to meet families we can all relate to, from those who just can't seem to save, to folks on the verge of financial meltdown. With practical tips and her no-nonsense approach, Mary helps them get back on track to find financial freedom.
